00:06:13.183 --> 00:06:14.270 align:middle line:90%
We know that.

00:06:14.270 --> 00:06:17.120 align:middle line:84%
We also know that we
are part of that field.

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:21.890 align:middle line:84%
We know that human
DNA actually interacts

00:06:21.890 --> 00:06:26.420 align:middle line:84%
with the photons of atoms, the
stuff this world is made of.

00:06:26.420 --> 00:06:29.690 align:middle line:84%
