00:07:28.130 --> 00:07:30.230 align:middle line:84%
It's interesting,
scientists have

00:07:30.230 --> 00:07:33.980 align:middle line:84%
found that here
on Earth, we live

00:07:33.980 --> 00:07:36.530 align:middle line:84%
in a world of very
high magnetic fields.

00:07:36.530 --> 00:07:41.080 align:middle line:84%
There's a very strong magnetic
field that surrounds the Earth

00:07:41.080 --> 00:07:43.280 align:middle line:84%
and there is a very
powerful magnetic field

00:07:43.280 --> 00:07:45.590 align:middle line:84%
