reflected either in our bodies

00:08:09.590 --> 00:08:11.390 align:middle line:90%
or in the outer world.

00:08:11.390 --> 00:08:14.630 align:middle line:84%
The magnetic field
creates a lag time

00:08:14.630 --> 00:08:18.020 align:middle line:84%
that gives us the
opportunity to really think

00:08:18.020 --> 00:08:20.780 align:middle line:84%
about the choices we
make, about the emotions

00:08:20.780 --> 00:08:24.290 align:middle line:84%
that we're creating,
to hone those choices

00:08:24.290 --> 00:08:29.130 align:middle line:84%
before they become a reality
in our world and in our bodies.

00:08:29.130 --> 00:08:31.100 align:middle line:90%
So it suggests that maybe--

00:08:31.100 --> 00:08:34.080 align:middle line:84%
maybe-- we're going
find ourselves

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:38.580 align:middle line:84%
at some future time in a world
where that magnetic field is

00:08:38.580 --> 00:08:42.240 align:middle line:84%
not so strong, where our
choices become reality almost

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:45.180 align:middle line:84%
instantaneously; where our
thoughts, feelings, emotions,

00:08:45.180 --> 00:08:48.609 align:middle line:84%
and beliefs manifest
almost immediately.

00:08:48.609 --> 00:08:50.400 align:middle line:84%
And if that's the case,
it would make sense

00:08:50.400 --> 00:08:54.630 align:middle line:84%
that we're learning to master
the consequences of our choices

00:08:54.630 --> 00:08:58.300 align:middle line:84%
now, in this world, in a
relatively safe environment.

00:08:58.300 --> 00:09:03.210 align:middle line:84%
