life look like if every fantasy

00:09:03.210 --> 00:09:05.760 align:middle line:84%
that you have; if every
passing thought, feeling,

00:09:05.760 --> 00:09:08.310 align:middle line:84%
and emotion suddenly
became manifest?

00:09:08.310 --> 00:09:10.440 align:middle line:84%
I think you can agree
that all of our lives

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:12.840 align:middle line:84%
would look very different
than they look today.

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:17.430 align:middle line:84%
So this relationship
between the biology

00:09:17.430 --> 00:09:19.740 align:middle line:84%
