them within the context

00:09:37.970 --> 00:09:42.370 align:middle line:84%
of the mystical teachings of the
past, the spiritual traditions

00:09:42.370 --> 00:09:47.060 align:middle line:84%
that have always told us that
there is a power within us

00:09:47.060 --> 00:09:50.630 align:middle line:84%
to change the conditions
not only of our bodies,

00:09:50.630 --> 00:09:53.520 align:middle line:84%
but of our relationship
to the physical world.

00:09:53.520 --> 00:09:57.560 align:middle line:84%
And it's these abilities,
this human potential,

00:09:57.560 --> 00:10:00.290 align:middle line:84%
that has been the
core of the mysteries

00:10:00.290 --> 00:10:03.680 align:middle line:84%
and the secrets that were
preserved in the monasteries,

00:10:03.680 --> 00:10:05.210 align:middle line:84%
in the nunneries,
in the teachings

00:10:05.210 --> 00:10:08.690 align:middle line:84%
of the shamans and the
healers and the curanderos

00:10:08.690 --> 00:10:10.170 align:middle line:90%
throughout the world.

00:10:10.170 --> 00:10:13.340 align:middle line:10%
I've had the opportunity
to experience

00:10:13.340 --> 00:10:16.010 align:middle line:10%
precisely these kinds
of teachings personally,

00:10:16.010 --> 00:10:17.750 align:middle line:10%
and I'd like to take
just a few moments

00:10:17.750 --> 00:10:20.540 align:middle line:10%
to share with you an
example of exactly what it

00:10:20.540 --> 00:10:23.780 align:middle line:10%
is that I mean here.

00:10:23.780 --> 00:10:27.890 align:middle line:84%
In the 1990s, I had a
number of opportunities

00:10:27.890 --> 00:10:30.530 align:middle line:84%
to visit the monasteries
and nunneries

00:10:30.530 --> 00:10:33.840 align:middle line:84%
in the highlands of central
China on the Tibetan Plateau.

00:10:33.840 --> 00:10:37.580 align:middle line:84%
And at that time, Tibet
was very accessible to me.

00:10:37.580 --> 00:10:40.280 align:middle line:84%
12 monasteries and
two nunneries and some

00:10:40.280 --> 00:10:43.820 align:middle line:84%
of the most mystical
caves of the yogis

00:10:43.820 --> 00:10:46.190 align:middle line:84%
preserving the wisdom and
the teachings of those

00:10:46.190 --> 00:10:48.330 align:middle line:90%
who have come before us.

00:10:48.330 --> 00:10:53.030 align:middle line:84%
So it was in these places
where I had the opportunity

00:10:53.030 --> 00:10:57.840 align:middle line:84%
to see something that I have
studied since my childhood.

00:10:57.840 --> 00:11:02.570 align:middle line:84%
It is the dwelling of an
ancient yogi, a mystical yogi.

00:11:02.570 --> 00:11:03.840 align:middle line:90%
His name was Milarepa.

00:11:03.840 --> 00:11:06.920 align:middle line:84%
His full name was
Jetsun Milarepa.

00:11:06.920 --> 00:11:11.180 align:middle line:84%
And he lived between
the years 1052 and 1135.

00:11:11.180 --> 00:11:13.630 align:middle line:84%
Let me tell you a little
bit about Milarepa's life

00:11:13.630 --> 00:11:15.830 align:middle line:84%
and it will help to
understand what it is

00:11:15.830 --> 00:11:18.040 align:middle line:90%
that he left in his teaching.

00:11:18.040 --> 00:11:21.740 align:middle line:84%
Milarepa came from
a privileged family.

00:11:21.740 --> 00:11:25.880 align:middle line:84%
His parents were wealthy,
his life was relatively easy.

00:11:25.880 --> 00:11:29.960 align:middle line:84%
He studied the mystical arts
because he had the opportunity

00:11:29.960 --> 00:11:32.510 align:middle line:90%
to do precisely that.

00:11:32.510 --> 00:11:35.510 align:middle line:84%
And it was during
his youth that there

00:11:35.510 --> 00:11:40.730 align:middle line:84%
was a battle between his village
and a neighboring village.

00:11:40.730 --> 00:11:46.070 align:middle line:84%
And his entire family was
killed in this battle.

00:11:46.070 --> 00:11:48.710 align:middle line:84%
His village was destroyed,
all of his friends,

00:11:48.710 --> 00:11:52.010 align:middle line:84%
his neighbors, everyone that
he had known were killed.

00:11:52.010 --> 00:11:56.000 align:middle line:84%
And he survived and became
enraged from within.

00:11:56.000 --> 00:12:00.260 align:middle line:84%
And he channeled his
rage into revenge.

00:12:00.260 --> 00:12:06.320 align:middle line:84%
He used what he knew of the
mystical arts to exact revenge

00:12:06.320 --> 00:12:09.590 align:middle line:84%
upon those who had taken the
lives of everyone that he knew.

00:12:09.590 --> 00:12:12.560 align:middle line:84%
He went and he took
many lives himself.

00:12:12.560 --> 00:12:14.600 align:middle line:84%
He killed the people
responsible for killing

00:12:14.600 --> 00:12:17.810 align:middle line:84%
his family, killed the people
responsible for destroying

00:12:17.810 --> 00:12:19.070 align:middle line:90%
his village.

00:12:19.070 --> 00:12:22.310 align:middle line:84%
And immediately, he knew
that what he had done

00:12:22.310 --> 00:12:25.910 align:middle line:84%
was not honoring the
mystical teachings as they

00:12:25.910 --> 00:12:29.780 align:middle line:84%
had been shared with him and he
felt very remorseful for what

00:12:29.780 --> 00:12:30.790 align:middle line:90%
he had done.

00:12:30.790 --> 00:12:34.130 align:middle line:84%
It was in that moment
that Milarepa renounced

00:12:34.130 --> 00:12:36.270 align:middle line:90%
his physical possessions.

00:12:36.270 --> 00:12:38.960 align:middle line:84%
He left the world
of comfort and he

00:12:38.960 --> 00:12:43.040 align:middle line:84%
went to a cave high in
the mountains of Tibet

00:12:43.040 --> 00:12:46.970 align:middle line:84%
to reconcile his
emotions, the guilt

00:12:46.970 --> 00:12:51.950 align:middle line:84%
that he felt for taking so
many human lives in retribution

00:12:51.950 --> 00:12:55.160 align:middle line:84%
for the loss of his
family and his loved ones.

00:12:55.160 --> 00:13:01.280 align:middle line:84%
He vowed in that moment to
stay in a cave of seclusion

00:13:01.280 --> 00:13:03.350 align:middle line:84%
and to spend the
rest of his life

00:13:03.350 --> 00:13:07.700 align:middle line:84%
honing his skills
only for good things.

00:13:07.700 --> 00:13:12.710 align:middle line:84%
He would no longer use his
abilities to hurt other people.

00:13:12.710 --> 00:13:14.420 align:middle line:84%
For the rest of
his life, Milarepa

00:13:14.420 --> 00:13:19.760 align:middle line:84%
lived in a series of caves
high in the Tibetan Plateau.

00:13:19.760 --> 00:13:22.940 align:middle line:84%
And the writings of those
who had the opportunity

00:13:22.940 --> 00:13:25.910 align:middle line:84%
to spend time with him
describe his condition

00:13:25.910 --> 00:13:27.140 align:middle line:90%
in very graphic terms.

00:13:27.140 --> 00:13:32.900 align:middle line:84%
They say he ate only the nettles
that grew near the caves.

00:13:32.900 --> 00:13:35.060 align:middle line:84%
They were very high
and chlorophyll.

00:13:35.060 --> 00:13:40.850 align:middle line:84%
The diet of 100% chlorophyll
turned his body green.

00:13:40.850 --> 00:13:45.020 align:middle line:84%
His skin turned green,
his hair turned green.

00:13:45.020 --> 00:13:48.860 align:middle line:84%
His clothing became
tattered and his hair

00:13:48.860 --> 00:13:50.360 align:middle line:90%
grew down to his waist.

00:13:50.360 --> 00:13:52.730 align:middle line:84%
And they say he was a
very frightening sight

00:13:52.730 --> 00:13:57.080 align:middle line:84%
to see this man with green
skin, green teeth, green hair,

00:13:57.080 --> 00:14:00.350 align:middle line:84%
and tattered clothing come
to the mouth of the cave

00:14:00.350 --> 00:14:02.670 align:middle line:90%
when visitors would go there.

00:14:02.670 --> 00:14:04.760 align:middle line:84%
But the point that
the story is this,

00:14:04.760 --> 00:14:10.160 align:middle line:84%
Milarepa mastered his inner
potential and the ability

00:14:10.160 --> 00:14:11.840 align:middle line:90%
to use it for good things.

00:14:11.840 --> 00:14:13.280 align:middle line:84%
And there were
students that would

00:14:13.280 --> 00:14:18.290 align:middle line:84%
come to him who wanted to learn
what it is that he had learned.

00:14:18.290 --> 00:14:21.440 align:middle line:84%
And Milarepa would use the
opportunity of this cave

00:14:21.440 --> 00:14:24.440 align:middle line:84%
to demonstrate something
for his students

00:14:24.440 --> 00:14:27.710 align:middle line:84%
that has great relevance in
what we're talking about here.

00:14:27.710 --> 00:14:31.370 align:middle line:10%
When pilgrims visit
Milarepa's cave today,

00:14:31.370 --> 00:14:34.010 align:middle line:10%
they see the remnants
of his teachings

00:14:34.010 --> 00:14:37.970 align:middle line:10%
that he offered to his students
and they see the remnants

00:14:37.970 --> 00:14:41.420 align:middle line:10%
on the ceiling of the cave
walls just as you're seeing

00:14:41.420 --> 00:14:42.810 align:middle line:10%
on your screen right now.

00:14:42.810 --> 00:14:45.260 align:middle line:84%
There are pilgrims
that come to pay homage

00:14:45.260 --> 00:14:49.400 align:middle line:84%
to Milarepa's teaching, but
there are students who come

00:14:49.400 --> 00:14:51.440 align:middle line:84%
and they literally
will place their hands

00:14:51.440 --> 00:14:54.230 align:middle line:84%
at very specific
places on the walls

00:14:54.230 --> 00:14:55.640 align:middle line:90%
and on the ceilings of the cave.

00:14:55.640 --> 00:14:57.740 align:middle line:90%
These are not random places.

00:14:57.740 --> 00:14:59.740 align:middle line:84%
Because what they
are doing is they

00:14:59.740 --> 00:15:04.300 align:middle line:84%
are placing their hands
precisely in the place

00:15:04.300 --> 00:15:06.380 align:middle line:90%
that Milarepa placed his.

00:15:06.380 --> 00:15:08.400 align:middle line:90%
Here's the reason why.

00:15:08.400 --> 00:15:11.360 align:middle line:84%
What Milarepa demonstrated
for his students

00:15:11.360 --> 00:15:15.170 align:middle line:84%
was that he would place his
hand against the physical wall

00:15:15.170 --> 00:15:16.060 align:middle line:90%
of the cave.

00:15:16.060 --> 00:15:19.970 align:middle line:84%
He would close his eyes,
take a deep breath.

00:15:19.970 --> 00:15:22.950 align:middle line:84%
He would create an
inner experience

00:15:22.950 --> 00:15:27.310 align:middle line:84%
within his body that
changed his relationship

00:15:27.310 --> 00:15:29.260 align:middle line:90%
with his physical world.

00:15:29.260 --> 00:15:33.730 align:middle line:84%
And to demonstrate that, as he
touched the rock of the cave,

00:15:33.730 --> 00:15:36.280 align:middle line:84%
he would continue
to press his hand

00:15:36.280 --> 00:15:39.190 align:middle line:84%
and his hand would
continue to move

00:15:39.190 --> 00:15:44.000 align:middle line:84%
into the ceiling of the cave
as if the rock did not exist.

00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:46.300 align:middle line:84%
What Milarepa was
doing was transcending

00:15:46.300 --> 00:15:49.090 align:middle line:84%
the limits of his
physical reality,

00:15:49.090 --> 00:15:51.250 align:middle line:84%
and he was doing
it by regulating

00:15:51.250 --> 00:15:53.980 align:middle line:90%
his inner technology.

00:15:53.980 --> 00:16:00.070 align:middle line:84%
When he felt the feelings, when
he created this inner condition

00:16:00.070 --> 00:16:04.870 align:middle line:84%
of being able to move his
hand through that rock,

00:16:04.870 --> 00:16:08.230 align:middle line:84%
the walls of the cave
were no longer boundaries

00:16:08.230 --> 00:16:09.700 align:middle line:90%
to his experience.

00:16:09.700 --> 00:16:14.530 align:middle line:84%
He was no longer limited by
the physical walls of the cave.

00:16:14.530 --> 00:16:18.850 align:middle line:84%
And as he demonstrated
this for his students,

00:16:18.850 --> 00:16:22.210 align:middle line:84%
what he showed his students
was that they are only

00:16:22.210 --> 00:16:24.580 align:middle line:90%
limited in their lives.

00:16:24.580 --> 00:16:27.670 align:middle line:84%
They're only bound in
their physical world

00:16:27.670 --> 00:16:31.690 align:middle line:84%
as long as their beliefs
create that boundary.

00:16:31.690 --> 00:16:36.160 align:middle line:84%
And by seeing Milarepa
transcend these limits,

00:16:36.160 --> 00:16:39.970 align:middle line:84%
it freed the inner
beliefs of his students

00:16:39.970 --> 00:16:42.000 align:middle line:90%
to do the same for themselves.

00:16:42.000 --> 00:16:44.260 align:middle line:84%
And I want you to
know the reason why.

00:16:44.260 --> 00:16:48.100 align:middle line:84%
It's because this ties
precisely into what we're

00:16:48.100 --> 00:16:50.770 align:middle line:90%
learning in our simulation.

00:16:50.770 --> 00:16:53.560 align:middle line:84%
How do we relate to
the laws of physics?

00:16:53.560 --> 00:16:56.770 align:middle line:84%
How do we relate to the laws
of our physical reality?

00:16:56.770 --> 00:17:02.890 align:middle line:84%
What is our inner potential to
actually transcend the limits

00:17:02.890 --> 00:17:05.650 align:middle line:84%
that we perceive in our
world and what might that

00:17:05.650 --> 00:17:07.240 align:middle line:84%
mean in the world
that we're going

00:17:07.240 --> 00:17:11.377 align:middle line:84%
to as we learn of our greatest
potential in this simulation?

00:17:11.377 --> 00:17:18.069 align:middle line:90%


00:17:18.069 --> 00:17:22.720 align:middle line:84%
So when we think about what
Milarepa showed his students

00:17:22.720 --> 00:17:24.990 align:middle line:84%
on the walls of
that cave, I want

00:17:24.990 --> 00:17:27.190 align:middle line:84%
to tell you I went
there myself personally

00:17:27.190 --> 00:17:30.920 align:middle line:84%
because I wanted to see the
legacy that Milarepa had left.

00:17:30.920 --> 00:17:34.410 align:middle line:84%
I physically placed my
hands into the impressions

00:17:34.410 --> 00:17:38.040 align:middle line:84%
that he left, multiple
impressions, in that cave wall.

00:17:38.040 --> 00:17:40.830 align:middle line:84%
Some of them came all
the way up to my mid-arm.

00:17:40.830 --> 00:17:44.090 align:middle line:84%
And my hands fit perfectly
into those imprints.

00:17:44.090 --> 00:17:46.170 align:middle line:84%
I'm absolutely certain
that this is not a hoax,

00:17:46.170 --> 00:17:50.610 align:middle line:84%
that this rock actually changed
its consistency in the presence

00:17:50.610 --> 00:17:53.850 align:middle line:84%
of this man's physical body
as a result of something

00:17:53.850 --> 00:17:57.280 align:middle line:90%
that he changed within himself.

00:17:57.280 --> 00:18:00.150 align:middle line:84%
So when we see something
like this, the question is,

00:18:00.150 --> 00:18:04.090 align:middle line:84%
is it a miracle or
is it a technology?

00:18:04.090 --> 00:18:05.700 align:middle line:84%
Well, the answer
to this question

00:18:05.700 --> 00:18:08.820 align:middle line:84%
depends upon you and how
you think of yourself.

00:18:08.820 --> 00:18:10.590 align:middle line:90%
What is your story?

00:18:10.590 --> 00:18:13.890 align:middle line:84%
What is your story that you
tell yourself and believe

00:18:13.890 --> 00:18:16.380 align:middle line:84%
about your relationship
to the world?

00:18:16.380 --> 00:18:20.340 align:middle line:84%
Do you believe that you are
limited in your experience,

00:18:20.340 --> 00:18:24.030 align:middle line:84%
that you live in a world
of separation, competition,

00:18:24.030 --> 00:18:27.374 align:middle line:84%
conflict where you are separate
from your physical reality,

00:18:27.374 --> 00:18:29.040 align:middle line:84%
where you're separate
from your own body

00:18:29.040 --> 00:18:31.860 align:middle line:84%
and powerless over
any circumstances

00:18:31.860 --> 00:18:33.160 align:middle line:90%
or conditions in your life?

00:18:33.160 --> 00:18:37.830 align:middle line:84%
Or do you believe that you live
in a world that is connected,

00:18:37.830 --> 00:18:39.720 align:middle line:84%
that is unified,
that you are part of

00:18:39.720 --> 00:18:42.750 align:middle line:84%
rather than separate from
the world that you see

00:18:42.750 --> 00:18:46.110 align:middle line:84%
and because of that, as
you change in yourself

00:18:46.110 --> 00:18:49.680 align:middle line:84%
from within that you can full
well expect those changes to be

00:18:49.680 --> 00:18:52.920 align:middle line:84%
reflected and mirrored
in your physical reality

00:18:52.920 --> 00:18:54.790 align:middle line:90%
in the world around you?

00:18:54.790 --> 00:18:56.640 align:middle line:84%
Well, your answer
to the question

00:18:56.640 --> 00:18:58.710 align:middle line:84%
determines the
answer as to whether

00:18:58.710 --> 00:19:00.930 align:middle line:84%
or not what Milarepa
showed us is

00:19:00.930 --> 00:19:03.930 align:middle line:84%
a miracle or a
technology helping

00:19:03.930 --> 00:19:09.030 align:middle line:84%
us to remember the potential
that lives within each of us.

00:19:09.030 --> 00:19:11.400 align:middle line:84%
Well, our own science
now is beginning

00:19:11.400 --> 00:19:14.550 align:middle line:84%
to reveal relationships
within our bodies

00:19:14.550 --> 00:19:17.430 align:middle line:84%
in just the last
few years that help

00:19:17.430 --> 00:19:20.640 align:middle line:84%
us to give credence to
what Milarepa showed us.

00:19:20.640 --> 00:19:24.210 align:middle line:84%
I want to share two recent
discoveries with you.

00:19:24.210 --> 00:19:27.180 align:middle line:84%
These discoveries are
so recent they're rarely

00:19:27.180 --> 00:19:31.470 align:middle line:84%
taught in textbooks and in the
classrooms on the one hand.

00:19:31.470 --> 00:19:35.040 align:middle line:84%
And on the other hand, they are
based in peer-reviewed science

00:19:35.040 --> 00:19:38.040 align:middle line:84%
and they tell us
something about ourselves,

00:19:38.040 --> 00:19:40.410 align:middle line:84%
and that something
changes the way

00:19:40.410 --> 00:19:43.770 align:middle line:84%
we think of ourselves and our
relationship to the world.

00:19:43.770 --> 00:19:45.480 align:middle line:84%
Now, the first of
these discoveries I

00:19:45.480 --> 00:19:49.110 align:middle line:84%
talked about in greater detail
in the first season of "Missing

00:19:49.110 --> 00:19:50.340 align:middle line:90%
Links."

00:19:50.340 --> 00:19:56.160 align:middle line:84%
In 1991, scientists discovered
approximately 40,000

00:19:56.160 --> 00:20:00.300 align:middle line:84%
specialized cells concentrated
within every human heart

00:20:00.300 --> 00:20:04.110 align:middle line:84%
in a way that simply had not
been recognized previously.

00:20:04.110 --> 00:20:07.020 align:middle line:84%
They're called sensory
neurites, which

00:20:07.020 --> 00:20:09.120 align:middle line:84%
is a little bit of a
technical-sounding word.

00:20:09.120 --> 00:20:11.280 align:middle line:84%
They're essentially
brain-like cells,

00:20:11.280 --> 00:20:13.900 align:middle line:84%
but they're not in the
brain, they're in the heart.

00:20:13.900 --> 00:20:15.750 align:middle line:84%
They are concentrated
in such a way

00:20:15.750 --> 00:20:19.050 align:middle line:84%
that they're actually called
the little brain in the heart.

00:20:19.050 --> 00:20:23.157 align:middle line:84%
And these cells literally
think independently

00:20:23.157 --> 00:20:24.240 align:middle line:90%
of the cells in our brain.

00:20:24.240 --> 00:20:27.480 align:middle line:84%
They feel and they
remember independently

00:20:27.480 --> 00:20:30.010 align:middle line:90%
of the neurons in our brain.

00:20:30.010 --> 00:20:33.720 align:middle line:84%
So what we're talking about are
two separate organs, the brain

00:20:33.720 --> 00:20:35.080 align:middle line:90%
and the heart.

00:20:35.080 --> 00:20:39.300 align:middle line:84%
However, we also know that
there is the potential

00:20:39.300 --> 00:20:42.090 align:middle line:84%
to harmonize the
heart and the brain

00:20:42.090 --> 00:20:46.320 align:middle line:84%
into a single potent system,
to harmonize the heart

00:20:46.320 --> 00:20:50.190 align:middle line:84%
and the brain through what we
call heart-brain coherence.

00:20:50.190 --> 00:20:54.900 align:middle line:84%
And when we do that, we change
our relationship to our bodies,

00:20:54.900 --> 00:20:58.680 align:middle line:84%
we change our relationship
to our physical world.

00:20:58.680 --> 00:21:02.490 align:middle line:84%
For example, when we harmonize
the heart and the brain,

00:21:02.490 --> 00:21:06.660 align:middle line:84%
we open the doorway
to self-regulation

00:21:06.660 --> 00:21:10.620 align:middle line:84%
of some of the most mystical
systems within the human body.

00:21:10.620 --> 00:21:13.260 align:middle line:84%
We open the door to
the self-regulation

00:21:13.260 --> 00:21:18.210 align:middle line:84%
of deep intuition, for example,
on demand, deep intuition when

00:21:18.210 --> 00:21:22.110 align:middle line:84%
we choose to have it, rather
than waiting for the universe

00:21:22.110 --> 00:21:26.927 align:middle line:84%
to simply surprise us
with spontaneous intuition

00:21:26.927 --> 00:21:28.260 align:middle line:90%
at different times in our lives.

00:21:28.260 --> 00:21:31.380 align:middle line:84%
We've all experienced
spontaneous intuition.

00:21:31.380 --> 00:21:33.810 align:middle line:84%
When you pick up the
telephone to call someone

00:21:33.810 --> 00:21:36.030 align:middle line:84%
that you care about and
they're already on the phone

00:21:36.030 --> 00:21:38.130 align:middle line:84%
before you dial
that number, that's

00:21:38.130 --> 00:21:40.570 align:middle line:84%
an example of
spontaneous intuition.

00:21:40.570 --> 00:21:42.570 align:middle line:84%
You had that
experience, and I know

00:21:42.570 --> 00:21:44.440 align:middle line:84%
we've all had this
from time to time,

00:21:44.440 --> 00:21:47.400 align:middle line:84%
